This is fun map I made. You spawn with just a TMP and Knives in a dust like area. Theres the outside open shootout level and the underground dark level. Theres also a grenade in the middle to make everyone rush for it. And a campfire in the middle of the underground level, shoot at it to light it up.

2/26/07 - I will be working on a newer more optimized version and overall better looking version of this map. This was one of my first maps and I look back on it today seeing how bad it was and lacking in details. Expect a new release.
Very little city.

:D This started as a joke of making a pig statue for a prefab, Uberkirsche gave me the idea but you don't want to know how. So it's just a big pig, buildings on either side of it and a lake infront / behind it. There's a slide going down from his snout and one from his ass. There's also a small ramp on his back that you can use as a launcher to launch you to the lake infront of him. So basically, its an all out knife fight where you can run in so many ways.

*Note* Piggy crushed a gas tank and it's on fire. :)

Bringing back the Jump maps.

Jump your way to the end of the map, if you fall you will be teleported to the nearest checkpoint.
At the end, someone will need to stand on a button which opens the door to let other people in, which means someone must stay behind.


3 large jump rooms and final/credits room where knives are located to pick up.
A song plays when someone enters the winner room, there you can teleport to checkpoints to play over again.


Have fun with my favorite map type, the old Jump maps!

This is a map created for the Christmas event of i3D on the 23th December 2011. After creating it in a very short time i created a fix (v2) that fixed most things.

Information that might help playing the map:
- There are 4 trucks, but only 2 spawnpoints, an admin can do swapteam and teleport to use more trucks if needed.
- The red numbers in the corners of T-spawn are buttons where you can reset the truck, in case of flipping over.
- You have roughly 3,5 minutes to kill all the cts before the nuke strikes and kills the terrorists.
- As terrorists you can use the horn of the truck using your left mouse button.
